<p />
<dt><strong>Requirements and Tested Browsers</strong></dt>
	<dd>
	<ul>
		<li>JavaScript Enabled Browser</li>
		<li>Any modern browser (tested in Firefox, IE, and Chrome)</li>
		<li>Goggle Maps works with most <a href="http://local.google.com/support/bin/answer.py?answer=16532&topic=1499">Modern Browsers</a>.</li>
	</ul>
	If you experience problems with a particular browser or operating system just <a href="mailt:dave@uesp.net">Let Me Know</a>.
	</dd>
